    <text>
        <div facs="#eSc_textblock_c5442680">
            <hi rendition="#c">
                <head>
                    <lb />The
                    <lb /><orgName>Welte Mignon Studios</orgName>
                </head>
                <lb />Offer you exceptional opportunities
            </hi>
        </div>
        <div facs="#eSc_textblock_a6014ae2">
            <lb />
            <hi rendition="#u">
                The Master Himself
            </hi>
        </div>
        <div facs="#eSc_textblock_b536deda">
            <lb />Not just mechanical playing of his compositions,<lb />but <seg ana="#virtual_presence" type="topic" resp="#np">his own fingers on your
            keyboard</seg>.</div>
        <div facs="#eSc_textblock_e56f4d74">
            <lb />
            <hi rendition="#u">
                <seg type="topic" ana="#touch_of_a_button" resp="#np">At Your Command</seg>
            </hi>
        </div>
        <div facs="#eSc_textblock_2389efb5">
            <lb />Accept as soon as you can our cordial invita-
            <lb />tion to spend a delightful hour or two with
            <lb />the masters of classic or popular music at our
            <lb />beautiful studios. We shall gladly play your fav-
            <lb />orite selections. We shall place at your disposal the
            <lb />services of a staff of musicians whose advice is al-
            <lb />ways ready but is never intruded. We offer a re-
            <lb />markable collection of instruments at reasonable
            <lb />prices and on exceptional terms.
        </div>
        <div facs="#eSc_textblock_2cbb468e">
            <lb />If <persName corresp="https://d-nb.info/gnd/118986724">Paderewski</persName>
            played to you, on your own piano, ex-
            <lb />actly as he played at the very zenith of his career when
            <lb />those marvelous fingers performed miracles, you could
            <lb />count it a great event in your life. This is what the
            <lb /><name type="brand">WELTE MIGNON Reproducing Piano</name> will do for you.
            <lb /><persName corresp="https://d-nb.info/gnd/118986724">Paderewski</persName>
            <seg ana="#soulfulness" type="topic" resp="#np">
                played his soul into the <name type="brand">Welte</name>
            </seg>,
            <seg ana="#immortality" type="topic" resp="#np">knowing<lb />full well that thus could he better pass on
            to coming gen-<lb />erations the perfect expression of his genius</seg>. It is the
            <seg ana="#soulfulness" type="topic" resp="#np">soul-<lb />expression</seg>
            that 
            <seg ana="#listening" type="topic" resp="#np">
                you feel when you listen to the <name type="brand">Welte</name>
            </seg>;
            and<lb />
            <seg ana="#repeatability" resp="#np" type="topic">
                you may hear it not only once, but
                as often as you wish.
            </seg>
            <lb /><persName type="artist" corresp="https://d-nb.info/gnd/118986724">Paderewski</persName>,
            <persName type="artist" corresp="https://d-nb.info/gnd/124379923">Lhevinne</persName>,
            <persName type="artist" corresp="https://d-nb.info/gnd/11918625X">Hofmann</persName>,
            <persName type="artist" corresp="https://d-nb.info/gnd/116014490">de Pachman</persName>,
            <persName type="artist" corresp="https://d-nb.info/gnd/118518011">Busoni</persName>,
            <persName type="artist" corresp="https://d-nb.info/gnd/11875081X">Saint-<lb />Saens</persName>,
            <persName type="artist" corresp="https://d-nb.info/gnd/118697641">Grieg</persName>,
            <persName type="artist" corresp="https://d-nb.info/gnd/118501437">d'Albert</persName>–156
            masters in all have
            <seg ana="#soulfulness" type="topic" resp="#np">
                played into the <name type="brand">Welte</name>
                <lb />for you the very essence of their musical
                personalities
            </seg>,
            <seg ana="#distinction_from_mechanical">
                for <name type="brand">Welte</name> re-
                <lb />production is not "stencil cutting,"
            </seg> but
            <seg ana="#exact_reproduction" resp="#np" type="topic">
                absolute tonal duplication.
            </seg>
            <lb />There are over
            <num type="cardinal" subtype="roll-count" value="5000">
                5,000 record-rolls
            </num> in the <name type="brand">Welte</name> repertoire. Come
            <lb />in to-day and hear your favorites.
            <seg ana="#affordability" resp="#np" type="topic">
                And bear in mind that the <name type="brand">Welte</name>
                <lb />is within your means, for it is sold on
                terms–your own within reason.
            </seg>
        </div>
        <div facs="#eSc_textblock_80803b8a">
            <lb />Our stock includes many examples of fine standard
            <lb />makes–
            <name type="brand">Welte</name>, <name type="brand">Estey</name>, <name type="brand">Conway</name>,
            and others–shown in a
            <lb />variety of case-designs and woods, giving you ample op-
            <lb />portunity to find the instrument that exactly suits your
            <lb />taste and means. We sell all grades (except "cheap").
            <lb />You can buy from us a really good instrument as low as
            <lb />
            <measure commodity="unspecified" unit="dollar" quantity="450">
                $450
            </measure>,
            on a series of monthly payments–terms, your own
            <lb />within reason.
        </div>
        <div facs="#eSc_textblock_b3e47c4c">
            <lb />Pianos and
            <lb />Player-Pianos
            <lb />at the Prices
            <lb />You expect
            <lb />to Pay
        </div>

        <div facs="#eSc_textblock_53814f97">
            <lb />WELTE TERMS</div>
        <div facs="#eSc_textblock_e007686d">
            <lb />We maintain that if music is to be
            <lb />enjoyed by everyone, it must be with
            <lb />in everyone's reach. So we placed
            <lb />every instrument in the <orgName>Welte
            <lb />Mignon Studios</orgName> just there–within
            <lb />EVERYONE'S means. Pick out any
            <lb />instrument you like, from lowest to highest price, and buy
            <lb />it on terms that are practically your own.
        </div>
        <div facs="#eSc_textblock_cd6fbfd8">
            <lb />A wonderful showing of Phonographs
        </div>
        <div facs="#eSc_textblock_4ba7b7ec">
            <lb /><name type="brand">VICTROLAS</name>
        </div>
        <div facs="#eSc_textblock_3c860cc6">
            <gap reason="irrelevant">
                <desc>
                    Advertises Victor products and models.
                </desc>
            </gap>
        </div>
        <div facs="#eSc_textblock_c69c9e23">
            <gap reason="irrelevant">
                <desc>
                    Advertises Pathe products and models
                </desc>
            </gap>
        </div>

        <div facs="#eSc_textblock_3838333f">
            <lb /><name type="brand">PATHE</name>
        </div>

        <div facs="#eSc_textblock_86963cd3">
            <lb />All the new <name type="brand">Victor Records</name> and
            <name type="brand">Pathe<lb />Discs</name> may be heard here as soon as they
            <lb />are published. Late "jazz" tunes, popular
            <lb />hits from current shows, the melodies every-
            <lb />one whistles and dances to, and those finer
            <lb />things constantly being recorded by great
            <lb />singers and instrumentalists. Learn to re-
            <lb />gard the <orgName>Welte Mignon Studios</orgName> as your
            <lb />place for hearing records. Drop in when-
            <lb />over you are "up the Avenue."
        </div>
        <div facs="#eSc_textblock_17b7db97">
            <lb />
            <hi rendition="#c">
                <hi rendition="#u">
                    <hi rendition="#i">
                        Can you drop in at once?
                    </hi>
                </hi>
            </hi>

            <lb />No matter how many times you've visited the <orgName>Studios</orgName> before this,
            <lb />come in again; there's always something new to see and to hear. Re-
            <lb />member that you are never pressed to buy–just come in as you would
            <lb />visit a famous picture gallery. But if you cannot come today or to-
            <lb />morrow; at least, send this coupon by way of getting information on
            <lb />the latest instrument designs.
        </div>
        <div facs="#eSc_textblock_d659d9d8">
            <lb />RECORDS</div>
        <div facs="#eSc_textblock_0eb08447">
            <lb /><orgName>The<lb />Welte Mignon Studios</orgName>
        </div>
        <div facs="#eSc_textblock_90b895ae">
            <lb /><address>667 Fifth Avenue</address>
        </div>
        <div facs="#eSc_textblock_d72e074e">
            <lb /><orgName>The Welte Mignon Studios</orgName>,
            <lb /><address>667 Fifth Ave., New York.</address>
